Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.60,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以千万不要随手丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:05.98,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\frz13.829\pos(867,67)}不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.60,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这颗满载梦想的心灵
